Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隱隱約約察覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我在蔻蔻面前不會笑一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔻蔻則為了掩蓋一切而永遠把微笑掛在臉上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約拿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 約拿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太突然了 真的是太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然沒電了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是該換電池的時候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不介意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還覺得蠻好玩的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道蔻蔻作為商人手段高超
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她像一個用不平衡的姿勢不斷全力衝刺的跑者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來有些危險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.63,0:00:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄完了這個也馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約拿小弟飛過來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩丟約拿小弟的遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看誰能丟得更遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約拿好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔻蔻 還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 人不是用來讓你們這麼丟著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和武器商人在一起旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:41.01,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have always stood on the borderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:41.01,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們始終踱步於境界線之上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.73,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enjoying the view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.73,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆因此境風景獨好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.35,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eeny,meeny,miny,moe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.35,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一，二，三，四...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:49.29,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,much the same
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:49.29,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:51.55,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have always stood on the borderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:51.55,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們始終踱步於境界線之上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:54.83,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enjoying the view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:54.83,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆因此境風景獨好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:15.33,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pike or shield?  負けたくはない　でも傷つけたくもない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:15.33,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矛 or 盾？ 不想認輸 可是又不願受傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.77,0:02:18.32,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手に取って　確かめてた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.77,0:02:18.32,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先挑一樣在手中仔細掂量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:20.52,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと戻れないんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:20.52,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是發現再要反悔為時已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:25.97,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:25.97,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選的是哪邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:28.75,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思い出は枷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:28.75,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思念是枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.27,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  後付けのlove
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.27,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  追悔莫及的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:34.08,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  優しさは仇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:34.08,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  溫柔是弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.44,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have always stood on the borderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.44,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們始終踱步於境界線之上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:41.13,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,広げる両手　keep balance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:41.13,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張開雙臂保持平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:46.36,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,より高く飛べる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:46.36,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著更高的天空振臂而飛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:56.01,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守りたいよ 僕らの翼のないこの背中に背負った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:56.01,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯獨想保護的是.. 背負於我們那折翼的背膀之上的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.30,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reality & Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.30,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實 & 夢想
